---
// src/components/WhyChooseUs.astro
// Section highlighting key benefits of shopping at EKOD Store
---
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">
      ¿Por Qué Elegir EKOD Store?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      
      {/* Beneficio 1: Calidad */}
      <div>
        {/* Placeholder for an icon */}
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-[8rem] w-[8rem] rounded-md bg-[#f59f58] text-white mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="h-12">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
          </svg>          
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Calidad Seleccionada</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Cada artículo en nuestra tienda es elegido por su calidad, durabilidad y diseño excepcional.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Beneficio 2: Diseño */}
      <div>
        {/* Placeholder for an icon */}
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-[8rem] w-[8rem] rounded-md bg-[#f59f58] text-white mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="h-12">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 0 0-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 0 0 8.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128Zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 0 0 3.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 0 1 1.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 0 0 4.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 0 0-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 0 0-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 0 0-3.42-3.42" />
          </svg>          
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Diseño Minimalista</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Nos enfocamos en la simplicidad y la funcionalidad, ofreciendo piezas que complementan tu estilo de vida.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Beneficio 3: Compra Fácil */}
      <div>
        {/* Placeholder for an icon */}
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-[8rem] w-[8rem] rounded-md bg-[#f59f58] text-white mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="h-12">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 10.5V6a3.75 3.75 0 1 0-7.5 0v4.5m11.356-1.993 1.263 12c.07.665-.45 1.243-1.119 1.243H4.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.12-1.243l1.264-12A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 5.513 7.5h12.974c.576 0 1.059.435 1.119 1.007ZM8.625 10.5a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm7.5 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Z" />
          </svg>          
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Compra Sencilla</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Disfruta de una experiencia de compra online fácil, rápida y segura desde cualquier lugar.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
